{"_path":"/maps/_ide/amp","_dir":"_ide","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Amp","description":"Amp 是一个 AI 原生的代码编辑器，强调 agentic workflow 和多种 AI 模式。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"deep-mode"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Deep Mode"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"smart-的协作-vs-deep-的独处"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Smart 的协作 vs Deep 的独处"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Smart 模式像一位热情的结对编程伙伴——急切、互动、随时愿意动手改代码。Deep 则是那种埋头苦干的工程师——沉默地读文件、在代码库里游走，可以独处五到十五分钟不被打扰。它不是在等待指令，而是在消化问题。这种性格差异决定了你什么时候该召唤谁。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://addyo.substack.com/p/the-70-problem-hard-truths-about","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The 70% problem: Hard truths about AI-assisted coding"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2004110489978953940","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人机结对编程已死？"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"deep-mode","depth":2,"text":"Deep Mode"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ide:amp.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ide/amp.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ide/amp","_extension":"md"}